  Game information:
  =================

  Set in 1960, the player assumes the role of a plane crash survivor named
  Jack, who must explore the dystopian underwater city of Rapture and survive
  the mutated beings and mechanical drones within it. The game incorporates
  elements found in role-playing and survival horror games, and is described by
  the developers as a "spiritual successor" to their previous title System
  Shock 2.
